snippet.title: Not Monday Cafe - Teaser trailer
snippet.description:
Not Monday Cafe 
Wishlist today on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3167540/Not_Monday_Cafe/

Idle cozy restaurant management game that sits on the bottom of your screen. Create and manage your dream café. Build and customize your restaurant, hire adorable staff, and unlock a variety of cuisines. Listen to jazz, chill, and transform your boring workday into a happy day.
